msg: Moved the default scripts injected into all widgets from a list of constants within StartPageProcessor into its own "feature", making it easier for admins to modify what gets injected into all widgets by modifying just the "widget" feature, for example to add things like usage tracking, common CSS definitions, swap out DWR for something else, etc. See WOOKIE-408.
